<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Workplace Bullying — <%- site.businessName %></title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/service-page.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>
  <section class="svc-hero"><div class="svc-hero-inner">
    <div class="svc-hero-content">
      <span class="hero-tag">Employment Law</span>
      <h1>Workplace <em>Bullying</em></h1>
      <p>Workplace bullying is serious, damaging, and unlawful. You don't have to endure it. We can help you take action against bullying behaviour and hold your employer accountable.</p>
      <ul class="svc-hero-bullets">
        <li>Your employer has a duty to provide a safe workplace</li>
        <li>Bullying can give rise to a personal grievance</li>
        <li>You can take action while still employed</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-hero-form">
      <p class="form-intro">Talk to us in confidence</p>
      <%- include("../partials/contact-form.ejs") %>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="svc-section svc-define"><div class="svc-section-inner">
    <div class="svc-text">
      <span class="section-label">Understanding the issue</span>
      <h2>What is workplace bullying?</h2>
      <p>Workplace bullying is repeated and unreasonable behaviour directed at an employee or group of employees that creates a risk to health and safety. It can take many forms including verbal abuse, humiliation, exclusion, threats, unreasonable workloads, or deliberate undermining of your work.</p>
      <p>In New Zealand, your employer has a duty under the Health and Safety at Work Act 2015 to provide a safe working environment, which includes protecting you from bullying. If your employer is aware of bullying and fails to address it, they may be in breach of this duty.</p>
      <p>Bullying can also give rise to a personal grievance claim for disadvantage in employment, particularly where your employer or a manager is the person doing the bullying, or where your employer fails to take reasonable steps to stop it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-callout"><div class="svc-callout-inner">
      <span class="callout-label">Important</span>
      <p>Keep a <strong>written record</strong> of bullying incidents including dates, times, what was said or done, and any witnesses. This evidence can be critical to the strength of your case.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Talk to us today</a>
    </div></div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="svc-section svc-help"><div class="svc-section-inner svc-section-inner--centered">
    <div class="svc-section-header"><span class="section-label">Our approach</span><h2>How we can help you</h2><p>We help you take action against workplace bullying while protecting your position and wellbeing.</p></div>
    <div class="svc-help-grid">
      <div class="svc-help-card"><div class="svc-help-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/></svg></div><h3>Case assessment</h3><p>We assess whether the behaviour you have experienced meets the threshold for workplace bullying and what legal options are available.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-help-card"><div class="svc-help-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg></div><h3>Formal complaints</h3><p>We help you make a formal complaint to your employer and ensure it is handled correctly under their internal procedures.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-help-card"><div class="svc-help-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/></svg></div><h3>Personal grievance</h3><p>We raise a personal grievance on your behalf where the bullying constitutes a disadvantage in employment.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-help-card"><div class="svc-help-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg></div><h3>WorkSafe referrals</h3><p>Where the bullying is severe or ongoing, we can assist you in making a complaint to WorkSafe New Zealand.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-help-card"><div class="svc-help-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 000 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 010 7H6"/></svg></div><h3>Compensation</h3><p>We pursue compensation for the harm caused including lost wages, stress, and humiliation where appropriate.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-help-card"><div class="svc-help-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07z"/></svg></div><h3>Confidential support</h3><p>We handle your case with sensitivity and discretion, understanding the personal impact bullying can have.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="svc-section svc-process"><div class="svc-section-inner svc-section-inner--centered">
    <div class="svc-section-header"><span class="section-label">Step by step</span><h2>What the process looks like</h2><p>Taking action against workplace bullying can feel daunting. Here is what to expect when you work with us.</p></div>
    <div class="svc-steps">
      <div class="svc-step"><div class="svc-step-num">01</div><div class="svc-step-content"><h3>Confidential consultation</h3><p>We start with a private conversation to understand what has been happening and assess your legal options.</p></div></div>
      <div class="svc-step"><div class="svc-step-num">02</div><div class="svc-step-content"><h3>Document the behaviour</h3><p>We help you compile a record of incidents and identify any supporting evidence such as emails or witness accounts.</p></div></div>
      <div class="svc-step"><div class="svc-step-num">03</div><div class="svc-step-content"><h3>Internal complaint</h3><p>We assist you in raising a formal complaint through your employer's internal process and monitor how it is handled.</p></div></div>
      <div class="svc-step"><div class="svc-step-num">04</div><div class="svc-step-content"><h3>Raise a grievance</h3><p>If the internal process fails or the bullying continues, we raise a formal personal grievance on your behalf.</p></div></div>
      <div class="svc-step"><div class="svc-step-num">05</div><div class="svc-step-content"><h3>Mediation</h3><p>We represent you at mediation and work to achieve a resolution that stops the bullying and compensates you for the harm caused.</p></div></div>
      <div class="svc-step"><div class="svc-step-num">06</div><div class="svc-step-content"><h3>Resolution</h3><p>We pursue the outcome that is right for you — whether that is compensation, a change in your working conditions, or a negotiated exit.</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="svc-section svc-restrictions"><div class="svc-section-inner">
    <div class="svc-text"><span class="section-label">Before you proceed</span><h2>Restrictions &amp; disqualifiers</h2><p>Workplace bullying claims can be complex. Here are some things to be aware of before proceeding.</p></div>
    <div class="svc-restrict-grid">
      <div class="svc-restrict-card svc-restrict-card--warn"><h3>Single incidents</h3><p>A single incident, however unpleasant, may not constitute bullying in the legal sense. Bullying is generally characterised by repeated behaviour over time.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-restrict-card svc-restrict-card--warn"><h3>Reasonable management</h3><p>Performance management, setting expectations, or issuing warnings — even if uncomfortable — does not constitute bullying if it is done in a reasonable and lawful manner.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-restrict-card svc-restrict-card--warn"><h3>90 day time limit</h3><p>Personal grievance claims arising from bullying must be raised within 90 days of the act or omission that gave rise to the grievance.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-restrict-card svc-restrict-card--warn"><h3>Evidence challenges</h3><p>Bullying often occurs without witnesses or documentary evidence, which can make cases more challenging — though not impossible — to pursue.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-restrict-card svc-restrict-card--warn"><h3>Still employed</h3><p>If you are still employed, taking action requires careful handling to protect your ongoing employment. We advise you on how to proceed safely.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-restrict-card svc-restrict-card--info"><h3>Not sure it qualifies?</h3><p>If you are unsure whether what you have experienced constitutes bullying, talk to us. Many people underestimate the seriousness of what they have experienced.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact"><div class="contact-inner">
    <div class="contact-info">
      <span class="section-label">Get in touch</span>
      <h2>You don't have to face this alone</h2>
      <p>Workplace bullying is serious and you deserve support. Contact us today for a confidential, free consultation.</p>
      <div class="contact-detail">
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 013 6.18 2 2 0 015 4h3a2 2 0 012 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 00.7 2.81 2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L9.09 11.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 002.81.7A2 2 0 0122 18z"/></svg></div><div class="contact-item-text"><span>Phone</span><a href="tel:<%- site.phoneTel %>"><%- site.phone %></a></div></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg></div><div class="contact-item-text"><span>Email</span><a href="mailto:<%- site.email %>"><%- site.email %></a></div></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg></div><div class="contact-item-text"><span>Address</span><p><%- site.address %></p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-form">
      <div id="form-success" class="form-message form-message--success" style="display:none;">Thank you! Your message has been sent. We will be in touch shortly.</div>
      <div id="form-error" class="form-message form-message--error" style="display:none;">Something went wrong. Please try again or call us directly.</div>
      <form id="contact-form" novalidate>
        <input type="hidden" name="service" value="Workplace Bullying">
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group"><label for="fname">First name</label><input type="text" id="fname" name="fname" placeholder="Jane" required></div>
          <div class="form-group"><label for="lname">Last name</label><input type="text" id="lname" name="lname" placeholder="Smith" required></div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group"><label for="email">Email address</label><input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="jane@example.com" required></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label for="phone">Phone number</label><input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="021 000 0000"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label for="message">Message</label><textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Briefly describe your situation..." required></textarea></div>
        <button type="submit" class="form-submit" id="form-btn">Send enquiry</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div></section>
  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
